---
// EstimationDeck.astro
---
<div class="glow-card">
  <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Select Your Card</h3>
  <p style="color: var(--text-gray-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
    Select a card to submit your estimate. The values are updated and shown in real-time.
  </p>

  <div class="card-grid" id="estimation-deck-grid">
    <div class="estimados-card" data-card="1">1</div>
    <div class="estimados-card" data-card="2">2</div>
    <div class="estimados-card" data-card="3">3</div>
    <div class="estimados-card" data-card="5">5</div>
    <div class="estimados-card" data-card="8">8</div>
    <div class="estimados-card special-card" data-card="Axe">Axe</div>
    <div class="estimados-card special-card" data-card="Diagram">Diagram</div>
    <div class="estimados-card special-card" data-card="AI">AI</div>
    <div class="estimados-card special-card" data-card="Coffee Cup">Coffee Cup</div>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color); padding-top: 1.5rem;">
    <h4 style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-white); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-weight: 600;">
      Card Guide & Meaning
    </h4>
    <div class="row g-3">
      <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
        <div class="legend-card" style="background: rgba(93, 82, 75, 0.03); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; height: 100%;">
          <div style="font-weight: 700; color: #6ab28f; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">1, 2, 3, 5, 8</div>
          <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-gray-light);">Story Points. Standard scale representing task size and complexity.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
        <div class="legend-card" style="background: rgba(239, 111, 111, 0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(239, 111, 111, 0.2); border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; height: 100%;">
          <div style="font-weight: 700; color: #ef6f6f; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">🪓 Axe</div>
          <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-gray-light);">Axe Protocol. Halts voting because the story is too complex or ambiguous.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
        <div class="legend-card" style="background: rgba(227, 141, 141, 0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(227, 141, 141, 0.2); border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; height: 100%;">
          <div style="font-weight: 700; color: #e38d8d; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">📊 Diagram</div>
          <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-gray-light);">Architecture diagrams, flows, or technical designs are needed.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
        <div class="legend-card" style="background: rgba(106, 178, 143, 0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(106, 178, 143, 0.2); border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; height: 100%;">
          <div style="font-weight: 700; color: #6ab28f; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">🤖 AI</div>
          <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-gray-light);">High technical uncertainty; seek AI assistance or prompt generation.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
        <div class="legend-card" style="background: rgba(226, 165, 74, 0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(226, 165, 74, 0.2); border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; height: 100%;">
          <div style="font-weight: 700; color: #e2a54a; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">☕ Coffee Cup</div>
          <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-gray-light);">Fatigue or deadlock; take a short team break to rest.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
